Carlos Di Sarli

Basically complete discography of 418 recordings by Carlos Di Sarli.

So what does basically mean? Some of the recordings with Mercedes Carné are missing:

  • Ay Jacobo, Orquesta Carlos Di Sarli con Mercedes Carné, Shotis, 1931, ?
  • Lupe, Orquesta Carlos Di Sarli con Mercedes Carné, Vals, 1931, Brunswick
  • Que lo larguen, Orquesta Carlos Di Sarli con Mercedes Carné, Tango, 1932, Brunswick
  • Soy tu esclavo, Orquesta Carlos Di Sarli con Mercedes Carné, Pasodoble, 1932, Brunswick

To my knowledge it is not clear that recordings of these performances exist. And those I was able to find are not useable qualitywise.

And most likely one of those which for me are difficult to identify:

  • No la maldigas por Dios, Orquesta Carlos Di Sarli con Jorge Durán, Tango, 11/1958, Philips
  • No la maldigas por Dios, Orquesta Carlos Di Sarli con Jorge Durán, Tango, 07/16/1958,
    RCA-Victor

In case you found missing or wrong information, or you might be able to help finding missing tracks - any feedback is very much welcomed! You may get in contact with me, or leave your comment at the end of this page.

If you are interested in one of the CDs mentioned get in contact with me, I might be able to get it for you. Of course you are also welcomed to take a look at my CDs on sale.

Please find more information about Carlos Di Sarli at Todotango.com.
